'''有机发光晶体管'''（{{lang-en|'''organic light-emitting transistor}}，'''简称'''OLET；'''也称'''有机发光敏晶体管）'''是一种新型的发光[[晶体管|晶体管]]。该种晶体管已被声称具有[[显示器|显示器]]和片上[[光互連|光互連]]的潜力。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://spectrum.ieee.org/semiconductors/optoelectronics/organic-transistor-could-outshine-oleds/0|title=Organic Transistor Could Outshine OLEDs|access-date=2016-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170207070331/http://spectrum.ieee.org/semiconductors/optoelectronics/organic-transistor-could-outshine-oleds/0|archive-date=2017-02-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>OLET是一种新的发光概念，可以采用标准的[[微电子学|微电子学]]技术轻松地集成在如[[硅|硅]]、[[玻璃|玻璃]]、[[纸张|纸张]]等基板上。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nanowerk.com/spotlight/spotid=16162.php|title=Organic light-emitting transistors outperforming OLEDs|access-date=2016-12-07|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125123140/https://www.nanowerk.com/spotlight/spotid=16162.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=意美聯合研發高效有機發光敏晶體管|url=http://scitech.people.com.cn/BIG5/11829217.html|accessdate=2016-12-07|agency=科技日报|publisher=人民网|date=2010-06-09|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220104056/http://scitech.people.com.cn/BIG5/11829217.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

OLET与[[有機發光二極體|有機發光二極體]]（OLED）的不同之处在于，有源矩阵可以完全由OLET制成，而OLED必须与诸如[[薄膜電晶體|TFT]]的开关元件组合。

